Genetic-Guided Pharmacotherapy for Atrial Fibrillation: A Systematic and 
Critical Review of Economic Evaluations.

Kamil AA(1), Lim KK(2), Koleva-Kolarova R(3), Chowienczyk P(4), Wolfe CDA(5), 
Fox-Rushby J(6).

Author information:
(1)School of Life Course & Population Sciences, Faculty of Life Sciences & 
Medicine, King's College London, London, England, UK.
(2)School of Life Course & Population Sciences, Faculty of Life Sciences & 
Medicine, King's College London, London, England, UK; National Institute for 
Health Research Biomedical Research Centre, Guy's and St Thomas' NHS Foundation 
