Generation, Selection, and Face Validation of Items for a New Generic Measure of 
Quality of Life: The EQ-HWB.

Carlton J(1), Peasgood T(2), Mukuria C(3), Connell J(3), Brazier J(3), Ludwig 
K(4), Marten O(4), Kreimeier S(4), Engel L(5), Belizán M(6), Yang Z(7), Monteiro 
A(8), Kuharic M(8), Luo N(9), Mulhern B(10), Greiner W(4), Pickard S(8), 
Augustovski F(6).

Author information:
(1)School of Health and Related Research, University of Sheffield, Sheffield, 
England, UK. Electronic address: j.carlton@sheffield.ac.uk.
(2)Melbourne School of Population and Global Health, University of Melbourne, 
Australia.
(3)School of Health and Related Research, University of Sheffield, Sheffield, 
England, UK.
(4)Department of Health Economics and Health Care Management, School of Public 
